{"tid":1292462,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"假Updates for Samsung軟件成功上架 引千萬人中招","createTime":"2019-07-07T10:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:34:32.000Z","uid":119778,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d156bab6d6e2ebfd1c4be4128e18db197523b464","tid":1292462,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScS6trs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScS6trs.png&h=4862b571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 是智能手機市場一哥，可能因為這個原因，騙徒睇準了 Galaxy 手機用戶人數眾多，竟然製作了一款名叫 Updates for Samsung 的 Android 軟件，並且成功在 Google Play 商店上架，這個並非由 Samsung 提供的軟件，縱使有數百負評，至今已經有超過 1,000 萬人下載。<br />\n<br />\n網絡安全研究機構 CSIS 的分析師 Aleksejs Kuprins 早前撰寫文章，表示 Updates for Samsung 雖然沒有惡意程式碼，但就會會引導用戶前往充滿廣告的網站，而且還會以欺詐方式，遊說用戶付費下載系統更新檔案。Kuprins 已經向 Google 舉報，要求對方將軟件下架。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/0707-2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F0707-2a.jpg&h=b425c3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUpdates for Samsung 軟件宣稱提供免費或付費下載 Galaxy 手機系統更新檔，不過網站不但充斥廣告，免費下載更限制在 56KBps，而且通過中途斷線迫用戶下載 34.99 美元的高級軟件包，以更快的速度下載。"},{"pid":"5415685cd7998a5dcb60c1e8d7727f020edb8907","tid":1292462,"uid":196924,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"要智力幾低先會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2217ad88a58d7c8433bcd0099483b75de558ee","tid":1292462,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"唔睇publisher 就download?"},{"pid":"1aa6fcc9b26a3c017d53bcf4a36e152411c236da","tid":1292462,"uid":65858,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"google play啲把關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7dd27dd94ece7be506c787e6be0fd311edb9ae","tid":1292462,"uid":653,"like"